    • MAX_TOTAL_CALL_NUMBER

      static final int MAX_TOTAL_CALL_NUMBER
      If an outgoing message has MatsTrace.getTotalCallNumber() higher than this (100), the processing will be refused (i.e. MatsEndpoint.MatsRefuseMessageException will be thrown).

      static final int MAX_STACK_HEIGHT
